snippet.title: Gigantosaurus: Dino Kart | Announce Trailer | UK | PEGI
snippet.description:
COMING SOON! The brand new #GigantosaurusDinoKart game! 🦖 Race around Cretacia, choose from 15 tracks and all of your favorite characters 🏎️ Full of awesome power-ups and obstacles and out-run dangers like hot lava eruptions from Mount Oblivion 🌋 Don't forget to lookout for #Gigantosaurus 🎮 Find out more https://outrightgames.com/games/gigantosaurus-dino-kart/
@Gigantosaurus @CyberGroupStudios
